Package de.braintags.io.vertx.pojomapper.annotation.field

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FieldState
    Defines the possible states of a field
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ConcreteClass
    By using this annotation you are able to define manually the Class, which shall be used to generate a field content from the content from the IDataStore
    ConstructorArguments
    Indicates that this field can be constructed from the stored fields; it doesn't require a no-args constructor.
    Embedded
    Specifies that a complex java object shall be stored embedded inside the IDataStore
    Encoder
    Specifies that the content of the field shall be encoded.
    Id
    Specifies the field, which shall be used as ID-field
    Property
    With this annotation one can specify, how a field shall be stored inside the IDataStore
    Referenced
    Signals, that a child object shall be stored by its identifyer inside the current field, the object itself is stored inside an own mapper
